                <div style="line-height: 1.6; color: #2d2d1f;">
                    <p><strong>ISSUE:</strong> Flavor enhancement insufficient</p>
                    <p><strong>SOLUTION:</strong> Increase deployment amount by 25%. Ensure even distribution across target surface.</p>
                    
                    <p style="margin-top: 1.5rem;"><strong>ISSUE:</strong> Over-seasoning detected</p>
                    <p><strong>SOLUTION:</strong> Dilute with additional unseasoned components. Remember: tactical restraint prevents mission failure.</p>
                    
