                    <p><strong>SOLUTION:</strong> Transfer to airtight container immediately. Moisture exposure reduces operational effectiveness.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Emergency Contacts -->
            <div class="section">
                <div class="section-header">VI. EMERGENCY SUPPORT PROTOCOLS</div>
                
                <div style="background: rgba(74, 93, 58, 0.1); padding: 2rem; border: 2px solid #4a5d3a; text-align: center;">
                    <div style="font-weight: bold; font-size: 1.2rem; color: #4a5d3a; margin-bottom: 1rem;">
                        24/7 TACTICAL SUPPORT AVAILABLE
                    </div>
