                        <strong>Field Support:</strong> support@rations-tactical.com<br>
                        <strong>Emergency Hotline:</strong> 1-800-RATIONS<br>
                        <strong>Recipe Intelligence:</strong> recipes@rations-tactical.com
                    </div>
